message.body: Well surprise, surprise, surprise... If we're the only 2 people left in this thing, shouldnt we have won the drawing by now?
Maybe..? Have you ever won? How do they let you know & send the money? How's your day? I had to work all day yesterday, & again today. So hot!
I won once, several weeks ago. They notified me by email and i had to fill out a w9 form but they havent processed the payment yet. I'm good. Just running
errands while i wait to get back to work. its nice to have some time to get caught up on local stuff after so long away, but i need to make some cash!
I hear you on needing the cash!
Nice to shower after a long days work, eh?
Yea, i seem to remember that feeling. No work again today, so I'm gonna head up to Tallahassee instead, see what these Dream Defenders are all about. Later.
